name: Copycat Finance
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: COPYCAT gives you the chance to invest in successful strategies of other master traders from all over the world. Use our leading copy trading engine building on DeFi technology to automatically copy their trading portfolio performance. With these 3 steps; Choose a master's strategy, invest funds and earn from every profitable trade.
